类 UserFacingMapState<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.state.UserFacingMapState<K,V>
  • 类型参数:
    K - The type of keys in the map state.
    V - The type of values in the map state.
    所有已实现的接口:
    MapState<K,V>, State

    class UserFacingMapState<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MapState<K,V>
    Simple wrapper map state that exposes empty state properly as an empty map.
